item.title: What's this all about?
item.description: All opinions expressed here are solely my own and do not express the views or opinions of my employer I’m Vaibhav Yenamandra and this is my (revived) blog. I work for Bloomberg L.P. as a software engineer on the Static Analysis and Automated Refactoring Team. I’d add a reassuring picture to convince you I am not an AI, but I don’t have one right now, so you’ll have to take my word for it.
